<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.3.7">
<l>kāṉār naṟuntuḻāy kaiceyta kaṇṇiyum</l>
<l>vāṉār ceḻuñcōlaik kaṟpakattiṉ vācikaiyum</l>
<l>tēṉār malarmēl tirumaṅkai pōttantāḷ</l>
<l>kōṉē yaḻēlaḻēl tālēlō kuṭantaik kiṭantāṉē tālēlō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The sacred lady [who sits] upon the lotus that is full of sweet juice</l>
<l>sent a garland of Kaṟpaka [flowers]  from the abundant groves of heaven</l>
<l>and a handmade chaplet of fragrant tulasi that flourishes in the jungle.</l>
<l>King, do not cry, do not cry, tālēlō! You who slept in Kuṭantai, tālēlō!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
